Writer:  Kevin Hill
Pencillers:  Albert Holaso
Inker:  Slick
Letterer:  Dave Vance
Cover Artist:  David Mowry, Slick, and Inferno Studios

Razor and Sade (the multi-pierced vigilante first seen in &quot;Rose &amp; Gunn #1&quot;) team up to pull the plug on Roman Von Drake's illegal skin trade. Raiding the Queen City docks, they make short work of Von Drake's security people and henchmen, but then have to take on the captain and crew of the inbound ship carrying new &quot;imports&quot; from Vietnam. Chief among their opposition is a bear of a man named Choi, the personal bodyguard of the captain and a merciless street fighter known for tearing his opponents apart with his bare hands.

Thanks goes to Talon for this release.

